sex research 
the two have collaborated delivering papers at conferences and 
editing a kinsey institute volume entitled 
masculinityfeminity published by the oxford university press 
in 1987 
reinisch and rosenblum both divorced have been engaged a long 
time according to reinisch but it has been kept quiet until 
now 
