became disoriented and didnt seem to know in which direction to 
swim ms russo was supervising the swim from the trawler 
we carried on a bit further but by now i was really worried 
and thought it had to stop the newspaper quoted cook as saying 
i looked over the side of the boat at the swimmer and i drew my 
hand across my throat to tell her to finish the swim but she took 
no notice the trainer assured me everything was all right 
