backlash in namibia because of preliminary south african proposals 
for independence elections that probably would result in government 
by the black majority 
the continental hotel was severely damaged by the explosion at 
about 7 pm witnesses said several parked cars were hurled across 
the street 
firefighters needed more than 90 minutes to bring the blaze 
under control the explosion apparently occurred near the hotel 
entrance witnesses said 
