<TEXT>
although many companies and banks lease planes 
to airlines a handful of specialized firms dominate the business 
worldwide the leading players are 
international lease finance corp based in beverly hills 
calif the company specializes in shortterm operating leases for 
aircraft it has a jet portfolio of about 60 aircraft worth 2 
billion with another 197 on order the company has 70 airline 
customers including major us and foreign carriers 
gatx air based in san francisco the company is a subsidiary 
of financial services company gatx corp it has fleet of 52 
aircraft plus 20 advanced airbus a320s on order the company has 
about 20 airline customers including nine outside the united 
states 
ge capital based in stamford conn the subsidiary of general 
electric co deals in leases of every kind mainly on a longterm 
